&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What the Role Is&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Babylist is hiring a Senior In-house Privacy Attorney to own and lead our privacy legal program. Reporting to the Senior Principal Counsel, you&#39;ll be the primary legal owner across U.S. state privacy compliance, our ads stack, product-embedded privacy, and AI governance. This is a strategic role — you&#39;ll be a direct partner to Product, Engineering, Data, and our Ads business, not a support function.&lt;/p&gt;
