&lt;p&gt;This is a fully on-site role at our Beverly Hills showroom. Please apply directly through this posting — to protect the guest experience,&lt;strong&gt; we ask that you don&#39;t call, email, or visit the showroom with hiring inquiries. &lt;/strong&gt;Thanks for keeping things smooth!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What the Role Is&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Babylist is hiring a Full-Time&lt;strong&gt; Showroom Host &lt;/strong&gt;to join our Beverly Hills team. Since opening in 2023, we&#39;ve welcomed expecting parents and their loved ones into a beautifully curated space to explore baby gear, build registries, and feel truly supported. We&#39;re looking for someone who is curious, empathetic, and excited to be part of our guests&#39; journeys. This is a permanent, in-showroom position (not event-based), averaging 35–40 hours per week with additional hours during peak seasons.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Weekend Availability is required&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who You Are&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2+ years in retail, hospitality, or guest service&lt;/strong&gt; — you know how to read a room and make people feel welcome&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A natural connector&lt;/strong&gt; — you build rapport quickly and genuinely enjoy helping people make decisions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Comfortable with product knowledge&lt;/strong&gt; — you&#39;re curious, pick things up fast, and can explain gear confidently&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A team player&lt;/strong&gt; — you show up for your teammates and contribute to a shared floor dynamic&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Operationally reliable&lt;/strong&gt; — you handle busy environments, shifting priorities, and closing tasks without being asked&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Physically ready&lt;/strong&gt; — available evenings, weekends, and holidays; able to lift 25–30 lbs and stand 8–10 hours&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;How You Will Make An Impact&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Guest experience&lt;/strong&gt; — greet and guide every family through the showroom with warmth and intention&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Registry support&lt;/strong&gt; — help guests build and manage Babylist registries that actually fit their needs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Product knowledge&lt;/strong&gt; — stay current on gear, safety info, and brand standards so every recommendation lands&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Showroom operations&lt;/strong&gt; — support events, pop-ups, inventory receiving, merchandising, and keeping the floor guest-ready&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Performance&lt;/strong&gt; — meet guest satisfaction and product knowledge goals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Content support&lt;/strong&gt; — collaborate with the social and content team on showroom moments where applicable&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Feedback loop&lt;/strong&gt; — share ideas that help improve the in-store experience over time&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
