&lt;p&gt;We pay competitive market rates.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Starting rate for this position is&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;$21.00 per hour&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
